{"tid":450406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傑青2017】 20歳南亞裔尖子  中學名列前茅 夢想港大讀醫　","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T04:43:02.000Z","uid":82646,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"db82d1ef1116882dce4ff012eb9e5593713c5a92","tid":450406,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"撰文： 林可欣<br />\n發佈日期：<span style=\"color: red;\">2017-08-20 00:00 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/777948/xlarge/eb936bff90ab7a2b0a0982a08a31c868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F777948%2Fxlarge%2Feb936bff90ab7a2b0a0982a08a31c868.jpg&h=52145996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘昌年原名不是姓「潘」，名字也非「昌年」，他其實叫Janis Khan，來自巴基斯坦。小子<span style=\"color: red;\">16歲</span>時離鄉別井<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">他的巴裔母親在港土生土長，20年前在家鄉誕下他。</span>他在巴基斯坦一個小村成長16年，四年前快要於<span style=\"color: red;\">當地升大學之際</span>，家人決定定居香港。原本的<span style=\"color: red;\">準大學生</span>來到此城插<span style=\"color: red;\">班讀中四，成績名列前茅</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前Janis最厲害的中文是應答考試題目。一般如Janis這類非華語生都會先應考相等於<span style=\"color: red;\">初小程度的國際試GCSE</span>（普通中學教育文憑考試）中文科<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">少數族裔考生可根據以上考試的中文科成績 經聯招報考本地資助院校。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4年前2013 移民時中四, 2017  20歲讀中六, 尖子? HK01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80/113159/%E5%A4%A2%E6%83%B3%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%80%E9%86%AB-%E5%B7%B4%E7%B1%8D%E5%B0%96%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%BE%97%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6-%E5%85%A5%E5%94%94%E5%85%A5%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%2F113159%2F%25E5%25A4%25A2%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%2580%25E9%2586%25AB-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E7%25B1%258D%25E5%25B0%2596%25E